movie_title: Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace
title: A Good Prequel Movie
review: I've seen SW:TPM, and I do believe this is a very good picture, despite all the merchandise, the story keeps you with a special interest about the true background of the Anakin Skywalker and their future role as Darth Vader, about how his fate will change the entire future within the Star Wars story.
